info.title: Canonn APIv2
info.description: An API for all the Science related information Canonn has in its datastores stored on the Gnosis, built using [Strapi](https://strapi.io) a Nodejs API framework.

servers.description: Beta Staging Server, should be used to test your application prior to deployment.
Live Production Server, should be used if your application has been tested and deployed.
Alpha Development Server, used by Canonn to test development prior to updating Staging and Production.
If you are running a local server for testing.
